  "summary": "Malicious code in solana-core-4 (npm)",
  "details": "Confirmed crypto-wallet/credential stealer published as solana-core-4 combosquat. Postinstall hook runs src/index.js which collects Solana/Ethereum/Bitcoin/Tron wallet key files, SSH private keys,.env secrets, and mnemonic/seed files, then exfiltrates all of them via api[.]telegram[.]org/bot[redacted-credential]/sendDocument to a hardcoded Telegram chat. Uses 4941ms setTimeout to evade sandbox detection. Publisher aicrypto-xzggz / an account is an account.",
